### Test API Endpoints for Allocat Budgeting App

# Replace YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN with actual JWT token from Supabase Auth
# Replace BASE_URL with your local development URL (e.g., http://localhost:3000)

### 1. Create Account
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Main Checking",
  "type": "checking",
  "balance": 2500.00
}

### 2. List Accounts
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

### 3. Create Category
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Groceries",
  "group_name": "Monthly Bills"
}

### 4. List Categories
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

### 5. Create Monthly Budget
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/budgets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": 12,
  "year": 2024,
  "to_be_budgeted": 5000.00
}

### 6. Get Budget Summary
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/budgets?month=12&year=2024
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

### 7. Allocate Funds to Category
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/budgets/allocate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "budget_id": "BUDGET_UUID_HERE",
  "category_id": "CATEGORY_UUID_HERE",
  "amount": 500.00
}

### 8. Create Transaction (Income)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_id": "ACCOUNT_UUID_HERE",
  "amount": 3000.00,
  "date": "2024-12-15",
  "description": "Salary",
  "type": "income"
}

### 9. Create Transaction (Expense)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_id": "ACCOUNT_UUID_HERE",
  "category_id": "CATEGORY_UUID_HERE",
  "amount": -75.50,
  "date": "2024-12-15",
  "description": "Grocery shopping",
  "type": "expense"
}

### 10. List Transactions
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

### 11. Get Spending Report
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/reports/spending?start_date=2024-12-01&end_date=2024-12-31&group_by=category
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

### 12. Get Net Worth Report
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/reports/net-worth
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN

### Notes:
# - Replace YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN with actual JWT token
# - Replace BASE_URL with your local development URL
# - Replace UUID placeholders with actual IDs from previous responses
# - All amounts are in decimal format (e.g., 1000.00)
# - Dates should be in ISO format (YYYY-MM-DD)
# - Negative amounts represent expenses, positive amounts represent income
